<br>
1) Is this staff this rare on the other servers ?<br>
<br>
2) any help to get the staff or suggestions ? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/urhionsligo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>rhionsligo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 258<br> <font color=#333333>(11/29/01 4:58:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=96.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.lehigh.edu/~dsf3/EQ/starofdavid.gif width=36 height=37></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Need help:</span><hr size=1> hell no it certainly isnt supposed to be that rare.  Late June is around when I started going to hate almost every day (i was in hate until mid september).  I was able to be in Hate and get steamrolled twice (he had the staff).  Two magi's later, he had a staff for me.  An hour later, another spawned with a staff for my friend.  And during those two months, 6 other mages got staves as well.  So I guess thats 6+me+friend+2steamrollers=10 staves in over 2 months.<br>
<br>
This is on Tarew Marr by the way. <p><img src="http://www.lehigh.edu/~dsf3/EQ/rhionsligo.jpg" align="center">
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/usvenalo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>svenalo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 122<br> <font color=#333333>(11/30/01 6:18:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=96.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Need help:</span><hr size=1> It is rare on Bertoxx because of our scheduling system...Hate is reserved by date, so the odds of the Magi being up when you go is low, and the odds of him having the staff at that time even lower. On servers where Hate is some place people just go to camp, you go up every three days or whatever and whack the mini's as they spawn, and someone should (assuming regularly getting the camp and a lack of KS'ing) get a staff (based on the rough averages - 90+% chance when mini spawns at least one will be a magi spawn, 30% chance that when he spawns he has it) within probably 4 or 5 kills.<br>
<br>
Rhion's experience is better than the averages I used (drawn from other threads)...two months is 60 or so days is around 20 spawnings (perhaps more if there were some multiples in a cycle). 10 staffs in that is 50% of the time he had a staff... <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=30883">
Svenalo</a>
